metadata.name: forced dance
metadata.description: Sometimes events and scenes occur in our social life that are repetitive to us , experienced them many times then touched the vicious circle time to time . Scenes that imprint in the darkness of our collective mind , that created Some rotary and interminable subscriptions , Sometimes there are remain silent, then we want to disremember them, Light shines from behind the darkness , they are become visible,  and by force We will have to watch the boring repetition again .
